== Askme.in Clone ==
Local Product Search Engine

Plugins Installed - PaperClip and Will_Paginate [Latest builds of both plugins from their github repositories]

Gems and Software required - RMagick Gem 2.5.2 and ImageMagick 6.5.8

Specify the path to ImageMagick in environment config file. [development.rb..]
 ======> Paperclip.options[:command_path] = "/usr/bin"  --> change it according to operating system		


Links =>

These links can be placed in the view files:-

1. Site Root/Home				<%= link_to "Home", root_path %>
2. Login Page					<%= link_to "Login", login_path %>
3. Logout Path					<%= link_to "Logout", logout_path %>
4. List of all businesses		<%= link_to "List all Businesses", businesses_path %>
5. Show a business				<%= link_to "Show Business Details", business_path( Business Id ) %>
6. New Business Form			<%= link_to "New Business", new_member_business( Member Id ) %>
6. Edit Business				<%= link_to "Edit Business", edit_member_business( Member Id, Business Id ) %>
7. New Member Registration		<%= link_to "Signup", new_member_path %>
8. Edit Member Details			<%= link_to "Edit Profile", edit_member_path( Member Id ) %>
9. Show Member Profile			<%= link_to "Profile", member_path( Member Id ) %>
10.Show My businesses			<%= link_to "Show My Businesses", show_my_businesses_member_path( Member Id ) %>
11. Show Favorite Businesses of a Member 		<%= link_to "Show Favorites", show_list_member( Member Id ) %>
